        </div>
        <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersH-I83"/>
        <p>A cruel hunter and roaming brigand, the <a href="ch67s06.html#MonstersH-I79">harpy</a> archer has trained as a fighter specializing in ranged combat. <a href="ch67s06.html#MonstersH-I79">Harpy</a> archers often become mercenaries, selling their services to the highest bidder. When not employed, they make ends meet as highway robbers, forcing merchant caravans to pay protection money.</p>
