            <p><span class="strong"><strong>Captivating Song (Su):</strong></span> Will DC 17 negates.</p>
            <p><span class="emphasis"><em>Possessions: +3 studded leather</em></span>,  <span class="emphasis"><em>+1 frost composite longbow</em></span> (+1 Str bonus), 10 cold iron arrows, 10 silvered arrows, 5 <span class="emphasis"><em>+2 arrows</em></span>,  <span class="emphasis"><em>lesser</em></span> <span class="emphasis"><em>bracers of archery</em></span>,  <span class="emphasis"><em>potion of cure moderate</em></span> <span class="emphasis"><em>wounds</em></span>,  <span class="emphasis"><em>potion of <a href="ch44.html#SpellsC6">cat's grace</a></em></span>,  <span class="emphasis"><em>cloak of <a href="ch49.html#SpellsP-R69">resistance</a></em></span> <span class="emphasis"><em>+2</em></span>,  <span class="emphasis"><em>ring of protection +1</em></span>. (Different <a href="ch67s06.html#MonstersH-I79">harpy</a> archers may have different possessions.)</p>
